&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;WORCESTERSHIRE ROYAL HOSPITAL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;AVON 4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;STAFF NURSE – BAND 5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;PERMANENT, FULL-TIME 37.5HRS PER WEEK&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;SHIFT ROTA&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a Staff Nurse on Avon 4 which is a 18 bedded ward including a dedicated 6 bedded dementia area and purpose built ‘Dementia Garden’. This ward cares for frail elderly patients who require transitional care to facilitate the discharge to their place of residence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The frailty service has seen some exiting new developments within the Trust recently with the new GEMS Service Team run by a team of Advanced Clinical Practitioners with a new assessment bay on the ward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be part of a dedicated team delivering a high standard of nursing care to our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome newly or recently qualified staff nurse with good communication skills and pride themselves on delivering quality care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comprehensive Trust and ward/department induction is provided and an established staff nurse development program is available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Informal enquires please contact – Patience Ngundu, Matron on: 01905 733782 or p.ngundu@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
